      <h2>Create a Student</h2>
      <p>All sessions and observations must be associated with a student. Therefore, the first step is to create a student. When completing the create student form, a user must include a student's first name and last name. All other fields are optional.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-xs-offset-0 col-sm-offset-0 col-sm-5">
