  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-xs-offset-0 col-sm-offset-1 col-sm-5">
      <h2>Create a Session</h2>
      <p>After a student record has been created, a user needs to create a session before collecting observations. There are two ways in which a session can be created.</p>
      <h3>Option 1</h3>
      <p>First, you can view the student record for the student whom you wish to observe. Then, select the "Create Session" button below the student record (as indicated in the image).</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-xs-offset-0 col-sm-offset-0 col-sm-5">
      <div class="tutorial-image-container">
        <p class="image-caption">Option 1</p>
        <img src="https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/13546265/25742308/d739d02a-315c-11e7-89de-74d61990e920.png" alt="Create Session Option 1">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-xs-offset-0 col-sm-offset-1 col-sm-5">
      <h3>Option 2</h3>
      <p>The second option is to go to the Student Record homepage where all student records are listed. Then, two steps need to be completed</p>
      <p>First, click on the "Create Sessions" button (Option 2 - Part A).</p>
      <p>After you complete this task, you will see a page which offers two options. The first is to create a student, which is required if there is no student record created for individual you will be observing. However, if a student record already exists,
        you can click "Existing Student". This display a list of all student records. From here, simply click "Select Student" for the row of the studen whom you will be observing (Option 2 - Part B).</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-xs-offset-0 col-sm-offset-0 col-sm-5">
      <div class="tutorial-image-container">
        <p class="image-caption">Option 2 - Part A</p>
        <img src="https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/13546265/25742658/6fcf66aa-315e-11e7-996b-0d438be16244.png" alt="Create Session Option 2a">
      </div>
      <div class="tutorial-image-container">
        <p class="image-caption">Option 2 - Part B</p>
        <img src="https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/13546265/25744197/8a9fa212-3166-11e7-8466-2c162d69f5ae.png" alt="Create Session Option 2b">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

